description:
In honor of "rights of passage," get pass through vibrations from the base of your energy center to the tippy top.  Each day of Burning Man at 10:30 a.m., Camp 88 will conduct a chakra-themed, 30-minute yoga session -- from the earthly, grounded energies below, to the spiritual, higher energies above.  Each day will include beautiful ambient music, and will correspond to one chakra: 
- Tuesday: 1st/root chakra; 
- Wednesday: 2nd/sacral chakra; 
- Thursday: 3rd/solar plexus chakra; 
- Friday: 4th/heart chakra; and 
- Saturday: 5th/throat chakra. 

The sessions will culminate in a final, 60- to 75-minute yoga and meditation session that incorporates the themes of the top three chakras: 6th (third eye), 7th (crown) and 8th (aura), centering on enlightenment and transcendence.  This final session will involve about 30 minutes of yoga, followed by about 30 minutes of silent meditation -- all set to intensely moving, deeply satisfying ambient music.

Retreat from the heat and the dust inside Ocean's Serene Luxury Spa @
Stardust Lounge Casino! We will be pampering our visitors with various
lotions and creams to rejuvenate their cracked and tired skin;
moisture wipes to clean off that brutal dust and dirt of the Playa;
comfortable lounge chairs; a cooling breeze from small, hand-held battery-operated fans; and, of course, hydration in the form of delicious cold water. Our guests will be able to adorn
themselves with temporary rub-on tattoos as a memento of their visit.
